title: Bjorn Setka is new world’s lightest 3D-printed, padded carbon saddle
content:
Over top of a fairly straightforward ultralight carbon shell & rails, Bjorn Cycles’ new Setka saddle 3D-prints custom carbon composite padding on top to add comfort without many extra grams. In fact, Bjorn says that their Setka is only the third 3D-printed padded saddle to come to market, and the lightest one yet… Bjorn Cycles

The post Bjorn Setka is new world’s lightest 3D-printed, padded carbon saddle appeared first on Bikerumor.
author: Cory Benson
